comment:
* Tracks the last fragment added and first fragment removed for fragment transitions.
     * This also tracks which fragments are changed by push or pop transactions.

variables.name: lastIn
variables.comment: * The last fragment added/attached/shown in its container

variables.name: lastInIsPop
variables.comment: * true when lastIn was added during a pop transaction or false if added with a push

variables.name: lastInTransaction
variables.comment: * The transaction that included the last in fragment

variables.name: firstOut
variables.comment: * The first fragment with a View that was removed/detached/hidden in its container.

variables.name: firstOutIsPop
variables.comment: * true when firstOut was removed during a pop transaction or false otherwise

variables.name: firstOutTransaction
variables.comment: * The transaction that included the first out fragment
